                                    <p style='font-size:13px;text-align:justify;'><strong><span style=''>* TI (Total Investment): Rupees &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; only per month for full month of working.</span></strong></p>
