                                        <li><span style='color:black;'>PT, TDS and such other statutory deductions would be deducted as per applicable norms.</span></li>
                                        <li><span style=''>PF &amp; ESI will be applicable as per the applicable norms. Once the Company will get the EPF &amp; ESIC registration under <span style="background:white;">Employees&apos; Provident Funds &amp; Miscellaneous Provision <em>Act</em>, 1952 and Employees State Insurance <em>Act</em>, 1948, t</span>he contribution against EPF, EPS &amp; ESI will be adjusted with your TI as mentioned above.</span></li>
                                        <li><span style='color:black;'>In addition to the above mentioned&nbsp;</span><span style=''>professional fee</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;color:black;'>, you shall also be providing a shared accommodation facility at company&rsquo;s guest house.</span></li>
                                        <li><span style=''>In case you are required to travel for hospital&rsquo;s work, the company will make appropriate arrangements, or you will be reimbursed expenses as permissible under the rules of the company.</span></li>
                                    </ul>
