                                    <p style='font-size:13px;'><strong><span style=''>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
                                    <p style='font-size:13px;text-align:justify;'><strong><span style='font-size:12px;'>Note:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style='font-size:12px;'>The above details are confidential and the same should not be disclosed / discussed. The Organization follows a fair and equitable policy for&nbsp;salary details;&nbsp;however a variation may exist due to varied educational qualifications, skill sets, time spent with the Organization, performance, etc., and the same is not open to negotiation.</span></p>


